<p>En posant β = (1 - α), β ∈ [0, 1] et en remarquant que <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle {\frac {1}{\alpha }}={\frac {1}{1-\beta }}=1+\beta +\beta ^{2}+\ldots +\beta ^{n}+\ldots }">
