<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle {\bar {x}}_{t}=\lim _{n\to \infty }{\frac {x_{t}+\beta \ x_{t-1}+\beta ^{2}\ x_{t-2}\ +\ldots +\ \beta ^{n}\ x_{t-n}}{1+\beta +\beta ^{2}+\ldots +\beta ^{n}}}}">
