      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle \scriptstyle -{\frac {2\pi }{\ln(1-\alpha )}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/410a504da8db6d13a579a6530a55e6e1449921a6" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.671ex; width:6.826ex; height:3.676ex;" alt="\scriptstyle -{\frac  {2\pi }{\ln(1-\alpha )}}"/></span> échantillons, la fluctuation se retrouve dans <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \scriptstyle {\bar {x}}_{t}}">
